{"tid":2226931,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"賴冠霖「在中國台灣等你」登央視國慶晚會　韓網震驚：認不出來！","createTime":"2020-10-02T11:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T12:44:25.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d80af4747002f21bcf02e551902fc598e92308","tid":2226931,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:15:57.000Z","msg":"大陸央視慶祝10月1日中國國慶，晚間播出《江山如畫國慶音樂會》，邀來許多音樂家、歌手演出慶祝。前韓團「Wanna One」成員賴冠霖在影片介紹中說道：「我是賴冠霖，我在中國台灣等你」，與李治廷、谷嘉誠演唱《龍的傳人更吸引大批網友死守直播，畫面也在韓網引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5179/d5179695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5179%2Fd5179695.jpg&h=9b0dfc70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲賴冠霖在央視國慶晚會演唱《龍的傳人》。（圖／翻攝自央視）<br />\n<br />\n賴冠霖錄製《江山如畫國慶音樂會》，穿著一身灰色西裝登台，和李治廷、谷嘉誠一起演唱《龍的傳人》。雖然他演唱的時間不長，但大批網友截圖上傳微博，誇讚「今天真棒！太帥了啊」、「小賴真的超帥，唱得真好」、「龍的傳人果然夠氣勢」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5179/d5179696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5179%2Fd5179696.jpg&h=1582fb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲賴冠霖為《江山如畫2020國慶音樂會》錄製幕後宣傳影片。（圖／翻攝自央視、賴冠霖微博）<br />\n<br />\n畫面傳到南韓知名論壇The qoo後也引熱議，文章中表示，賴冠霖就曾在微博上表示「我支持香港警察」，因此被大陸網友稱讚是「愛國青年」。更有南韓網友神解：「如果不理解是什麼意思，大概就是在大韓民國的親日派。」<br />\n<br />\n由於賴冠霖從Wanna One解散後，就將工作重心轉到大陸，已經久未在南韓演藝圈出現。不少南韓網友震驚表示：「天啊，這張臉已經不像是我認識的賴冠霖了。」、「是造型問題嗎？覺得跟在《Produce 101》時期看到的差好多。」、「這髮型怎麼回事？」、「造型感覺好老土。」討論留言超過6000條。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5179/d5179694.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5179%2Fd5179694.jpg&h=57a7fcee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲賴冠霖央視國慶晚會造型在韓網引起熱議。（圖／翻攝自The qoo）"},{"pid":"aa74206314f28f031e67c94c13839c93af88639b","tid":2226931,"uid":210112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"醜 拉"},{"pid":"bfc811f2d46e4a995f4eb451357e7a8c65e6bdbc","tid":2226931,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"奀星?"},{"pid":"d6b030776471889b41621a5d86d2f4b967b8e505","tid":2226931,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"而家成個支那仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前嘅賴冠霖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2aL1GDe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2aL1GDe.jpg&h=77fdb9ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c0ce2a5aa353920fef447dd5e604859e6556b17","tid":2226931,"uid":264426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3acf535ca21b97e16d04e2ee26e67d1c3d22b12","tid":2226931,"uid":68678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>17年6月有份投票/支持佢嘅所有人全部中肺炎死🙏🏻🙏🏻🤙🏻</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"19446bc2df6e7ebc7dc3d20550984572df8b0e2b","tid":2226931,"uid":7585,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6b030776471889b41621a5d86d2f4b967b8e505","tid":2226931,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"而家成個支那仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前嘅賴冠霖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2aL1GDe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2aL1GDe.jpg&h=77fdb9ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n依家個樣好樣過以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b8dbf21512ebdfed1ec88045e5bcae613ef1bd","tid":2226931,"uid":75372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d6b030776471889b41621a5d86d2f4b967b8e505","tid":2226931,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T11:26:41